<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 16:09:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>从哈马斯囚禁中获救的以色列人质回家庆祝他小儿子的一岁生日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-rescued-from-hamas-captivity-is-home-for-his-youngest-sons-first-birthday/00000191-989e-d222-a797-9e9fc2ac0000</link><description>以色列国防军部队在一个地下大院进行搜查后，人们普遍怀疑哈马斯人质可能藏身其中，凯德·法尔汉·埃尔卡迪被单独找到。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 14:45:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-rescued-from-hamas-captivity-is-home-for-his-youngest-sons-first-birthday/00000191-989e-d222-a797-9e9fc2ac0000</guid></item><item><title>“生活就像地狱”：约旦河西岸旅游之都伯利恒变成鬼城</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/life-has-been-hell-inside-bethlehem-the-west-banks-tourism-capital-turned-ghost-town/00000191-97e9-d13a-ab93-dfff37850000</link><description>巴勒斯坦城市伯利恒每年都会接待多达 150 万名游客。以色列-加沙战争对其造成了毁灭性影响，游客纷纷远离，出租车司机称他们平均每天的收入相当于一包香烟</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 14:32:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/life-has-been-hell-inside-bethlehem-the-west-banks-tourism-capital-turned-ghost-town/00000191-97e9-d13a-ab93-dfff37850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙南部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-combat/00000191-9862-df0a-ab9f-f96b0c550000</link><description>来自奥尔耶胡达的 19 岁中士阿米特·弗里德曼 (Amit Friedman) 是自战争开始以来第 703 名阵亡士兵。他在加沙地带南部与武装分子交火中身亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 14:32:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-combat/00000191-9862-df0a-ab9f-f96b0c550000</guid></item><item><title>无视高等法院和总检察长，以色列正在加速走向宪法危机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-is-racing-toward-a-constitutional-crisis/00000191-9473-df0a-ab9f-f57ba50a0000</link><description>以色列政府无视高等法院的裁决并不是什么新鲜事，但专家表示，这种趋势近年来有愈演愈烈的趋势。与此同时，部长们一再拒绝接受总检察长具有约束力的意见，并对她公开敌视，这是前所未有的</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 13:47:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-is-racing-toward-a-constitutional-crisis/00000191-9473-df0a-ab9f-f57ba50a0000</guid></item><item><title>卖淫不是一种选择，语言应该反映出这一点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/prostitution-isnt-a-choice-and-language-should-reflect-that/00000191-98c2-db54-a7d3-d9c346fc0000</link><description>以色列的一项新举措提供了一个词汇，帮助媒体更道德地报道卖淫，将焦点转移到皮条客和嫖客的活动上</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 12:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/prostitution-isnt-a-choice-and-language-should-reflect-that/00000191-98c2-db54-a7d3-d9c346fc0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷圣殿山/阿克萨圣殿的“现状”是什么？为什么如此不稳定？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-is-the-status-quo-at-jerusalems-temple-mount-al-aqsa-and-why-is-it-so-precarious/00000191-94d5-d13a-ab93-dcf75dfd0000</link><description>圣殿山/阿克萨大院是犹太教和穆斯林圣地的所在地，得益于自 1967 年以来一直保持不变的政策，圣殿山/阿克萨大院保持了两种宗教之间脆弱的和平。极右翼部长本-格维尔一直表示以色列的政策已经改变。这会产生什么影响？国土报解释</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:56:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-is-the-status-quo-at-jerusalems-temple-mount-al-aqsa-and-why-is-it-so-precarious/00000191-94d5-d13a-ab93-dcf75dfd0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人报告以色列军队在约旦河西岸的袭击中造成九人死亡、八人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-report-nine-killed-eight-wounded-in-israeli-army-west-bank-raids/00000191-97e9-df0a-ab9f-f7e97b7d0000</link><description>以色列军队同时开展了两项反恐行动，使用无人机并限制进入医院。以色列外交部长将此次袭击比作加沙行动，称以色列应考虑“在约旦河西岸临时撤离”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 09:24:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-report-nine-killed-eight-wounded-in-israeli-army-west-bank-raids/00000191-97e9-df0a-ab9f-f7e97b7d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列团队前往卡塔尔参加加沙谈判；资料来源：“除非内塔尼亚胡灵活，否则不会达成协议”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-heads-to-qatar-for-gaza-cease-fire-talks/00000191-9666-dd8c-addd-bff6357d0000</link><description>以色列派遣代表团这一事实表明各方都致力于这一进程，但以色列消息人士称，内塔尼亚胡的“红线问题”——费城路线和拉法过境点——没有取得进展</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 03:02:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-heads-to-qatar-for-gaza-cease-fire-talks/00000191-9666-dd8c-addd-bff6357d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军士兵在加沙丧生；陆军调查称定居者对吉特的袭击是“恐怖主义”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article-live/israel-launches-counterterror-op-in-west-bank-palestinians-say-at-least-four-killed/00000191-96c7-d13a-ab93-def775cb0000</link><description>美国制裁约旦河西岸定居点和定居者组织的安全负责人 ■ 以色列国防军表示，他们在叙利亚和黎巴嫩边境杀害了伊斯兰圣战组织高级成员 ■ 人质家属在特拉维夫集会寻求达成协议 ■ 以色列士兵在黎巴嫩边境附近的无人机袭击中受轻伤 ■ 部长雷格夫违反军事审查制度，公布救援地点 ■ 白宫：如果伊朗发动袭击，美国将保卫以色列</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 02:29:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article-live/israel-launches-counterterror-op-in-west-bank-palestinians-say-at-least-four-killed/00000191-96c7-d13a-ab93-def775cb0000</guid></item><item><title>担心伊朗报复袭击，美国在该地区保留两艘航母</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/concerned-about-iranian-revenge-attack-u-s-keeps-two-aircraft-carriers-in-region/00000191-953f-d302-add5-9fbf55cd0000</link><description>在真主党周日的袭击遭到挫败后，拜登政府仍然对伊朗对德黑兰伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚遇刺事件的反应感到担忧，并加强了在该地区的海军和空中舰队的部署，同时向以色列紧急运送武器</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 22:30:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/concerned-about-iranian-revenge-attack-u-s-keeps-two-aircraft-carriers-in-region/00000191-953f-d302-add5-9fbf55cd0000</guid></item><item><title>雷格夫驳斥批评，拒绝改变以色列10月7日纪念仪式计划的呼吁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/regev-rejects-calls-to-change-israels-plans-for-october-7-memorial-ceremony/00000191-9500-d13a-ab93-ddb731300000</link><description>交通部长表示，原计划的仪式没有任何改变，仪式将在没有观众的情况下现场直播，并包括预先录制的视频</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 20:46:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/regev-rejects-calls-to-change-israels-plans-for-october-7-memorial-ceremony/00000191-9500-d13a-ab93-ddb731300000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部门规划圣殿山导游服务；国家安全委员会尚未回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministry-planning-temple-mount-tours-national-security-council-yet-to-respond/00000191-9538-d60a-a395-bdbd6da50000</link><description>以色列遗产部表示，参观的内容将受到监控，以避免“为了推进反犹太议程而编写的另类事实和巴勒斯坦叙述”。总理办公室证实国家安全委员会尚未批准该倡议</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 20:13:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministry-planning-temple-mount-tours-national-security-council-yet-to-respond/00000191-9538-d60a-a395-bdbd6da50000</guid></item><item><title>发育不良、失败、可怕：内塔尼亚胡政府纪念 10 月 7 日周年纪念的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-27/ty-article/.highlight/stunted-failed-horrifying-the-netanyahu-governments-plan-to-mark-october-7-anniversary/00000191-9480-dd8c-addd-bdf4ddce0000</link><description>交通部长米里·雷格夫正在推进的 10 月 7 日国家仪式将完美地体现内塔尼亚胡政府对当天遭受最大损失的人们的不受欢迎、情绪低落的行为和失败</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 19:04:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-27/ty-article/.highlight/stunted-failed-horrifying-the-netanyahu-governments-plan-to-mark-october-7-anniversary/00000191-9480-dd8c-addd-bdf4ddce0000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟外长博雷尔要求对本格维尔和斯莫特里奇实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/eu-foreign-minister-borell-to-ask-for-sanctions-against-ben-gvir-smotrich/00000191-94a9-df0a-ab9f-f5a9b24f0000</link><description>博雷尔的请求需要所有27个欧盟成员国的批准，他们一致同意的可能性很低，但一些国家可能会选择独立推进此类制裁</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 17:35:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/eu-foreign-minister-borell-to-ask-for-sanctions-against-ben-gvir-smotrich/00000191-94a9-df0a-ab9f-f5a9b24f0000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯绑架的以色列青少年讲述加沙被囚禁的经历</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/israeli-teen-kidnapped-by-hamas-recounts-gaza-captivity/00000191-9483-dc4a-a59b-b6ab0fbe0000</link><description>阿加姆·戈尔茨坦-阿尔莫格在《华盛顿邮报》发表的一篇评论文章中透露，她在加沙的 51 天期间被迫背诵伊斯兰祈祷词</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 17:12:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/israeli-teen-kidnapped-by-hamas-recounts-gaza-captivity/00000191-9483-dc4a-a59b-b6ab0fbe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质逃离加沙绑架者，由以色列国防军送回以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-escaped-gaza-captors-returned-to-israel-by-idf/00000191-943e-d60a-a395-bcbfc4f90000</link><description>52 岁的凯德·法尔汉·埃尔卡迪 (Kaid Farhan Elkadi) 被关押在加沙南部的一个隧道中。他逃跑后遇到的士兵没有遇到绑架者，也没有在该地区找到其他人质。埃尔卡迪被送往的索罗卡医疗中心表示，他的状况良好</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 16:48:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-escaped-gaza-captors-returned-to-israel-by-idf/00000191-943e-d60a-a395-bcbfc4f90000</guid></item><item><title>“这是一个犹太复国主义频道”：10 月 7 日是否改变了沙特新闻频道 Al Arabiya？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-08-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/has-october-7-changed-saudi-news-channel-al-arabiya/00000191-8f20-dc4a-a59b-bfa88d7c0000</link><description>从让以色列军队发言人重复发言到用尖锐的问题攻击哈马斯领导人：了解沙特阿拉伯半岛电视台的替代者阿拉伯电视台</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 16:46:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-08-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/has-october-7-changed-saudi-news-channel-al-arabiya/00000191-8f20-dc4a-a59b-bfa88d7c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列全体反对派现在应该辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-entire-opposition-should-resign-now/00000191-93ba-dd8c-addd-bbfe47ee0000</link><description>如果以色列政客确实认识到存在的危险，并在这个决定性的“魏玛时刻”站起来反对极端主义内塔尼亚胡政府，这将是他们第一次、最后一次也是唯一真正的政治反对行为</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 16:35:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-entire-opposition-should-resign-now/00000191-93ba-dd8c-addd-bbfe47ee0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第326天：美国高级将领表示，中东全面战争的风险已经降低</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-326-risk-of-all-out-mideast-war-has-eased-top-u-s-general-says/00000191-9463-dd8c-addd-bdf781dd0000</link><description>被扣押在哈马斯隧道中的以色列人质逃离绑架者后被以色列国防军救出 ■ 巴勒斯坦医疗官员告诉《国土报》，如果加沙停火得不到落实，将很难为加沙儿童开展脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种活动 ■ 以色列定居者枪杀一名巴勒斯坦人并在伯利恒打伤另外三人 ■ 战争开始 326 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 16:31:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-326-risk-of-all-out-mideast-war-has-eased-top-u-s-general-says/00000191-9463-dd8c-addd-bdf781dd0000</guid></item><item><title>精疲力竭的黎巴嫩无法对真主党发起公民不服从</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/an-exhausted-lebanon-cant-mount-civil-disobedience-against-hezbollah/00000191-9397-d13a-ab93-dbb7aa340000</link><description>黎巴嫩正处于多层面的危机之中，以色列“将其送入石器时代”的威胁遭到了人们的质疑，因为许多黎巴嫩人认为他们已经进入了石器时代。黎巴嫩人民以前也曾奋起反抗，但真主党装备精良、支持充足，难以受到挑战</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 14:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/an-exhausted-lebanon-cant-mount-civil-disobedience-against-hezbollah/00000191-9397-d13a-ab93-dbb7aa340000</guid></item></channel></rss>